the player's three-pointer ability and free throw ability from the player's score, nor can we simply determine the player's o\x1Bensive ability from the assist data. A single indicator has its irreplaceable role, but its limitations determine that it cannot make an objective and comprehensive evaluation of the comprehensive ability of basketball players. Therefore, this dissertation will select appropriate summaries and use Latent variable model and an optimisation function algorithm to calculate the player's overall ability after each game, and then develop a adjustable workflow from reading and processing, modelling to the \x1Cnal display of results.")));
